A  - It's a bug found in CS:S. Right-Click the server, Click on 'Details', Copy the address( Looks Like : XXX.XXX.XXX.XXX:XXXX ). Open up the console( press ` ), Type "Connect {PAST ADDRESS HERE}" and hit enter.
